metadata.name: Elder Apes Yacht Club #1
metadata.description: The Grampa Ape Yacht Club NFT collection is a unique and highly sought-after series of digital assets that celebrates the playful and adventurous spirit of the ape community. Each NFT in the collection features a whimsical depiction of Grampa Ape, a beloved elder of the Yacht Club who has seen and done it all. From sailing the high seas to exploring exotic lands, Grampa Ape has led an extraordinary life, and now collectors have the opportunity to own a piece of his legacy.
